# Planning Gate

Before editing code or format specs for non-trivial work, produce a short plan that is explicit and checkable.

Required pre-edit checklist:

- Requirements and success criteria restated (milestone + spec section).
- Files expected to change are listed.
- Boundary and invariants listed (NGB I1–I6 when touching format/tools).
- Verification plan listed (scripts from milestone-gate).
- Rollback note for format version bumps.

Execution rule:

- Do not edit until the checklist is present in the chat update.
- If scope changes materially, refresh the checklist before continuing.
